ZH: 昨天晚上发生了一次海啸。
EN: A tsunami occurred last night.

ZH: 海啸预警已经发布。
EN: A tsunami warning has been issued.

ZH: 这个地区经常发生海啸。
EN: Tsunamis frequently occur in this area.

ZH: 海啸造成了数十人失踪。
EN: The tsunami caused dozens of people to go missing.

ZH: 我们必须尽快疏散，以免被海啸袭击。
EN: We must evacuate quickly to avoid being hit by a tsunami.

ZH: 他们成功逃过了海啸的袭击。
EN: They managed to escape the tsunami attack.

ZH: 这次海啸的威力非常巨大。
EN: The power of this tsunami is immense.

ZH: 海啸带来了海水和泥沙。
EN: The tsunami brought seawater and mud.

ZH: 人们四处奔逃以躲避海啸。
EN: People fled in all directions to escape the tsunami.

ZH: 海啸将整个小岛淹没了。
EN: The tsunami submerges the entire island.

ZH: 他们听到了海啸的警报，立即逃离沿海地区。
EN: They heard the tsunami warning and immediately fled the coastal areas.

ZH: 海啸的破坏范围非常广泛。
EN: The destruction caused by the tsunami is extensive.

ZH: 政府已经展开救援行动，帮助受灾群众。
EN: The government has initiated rescue operations to help the victims of the tsunami.

ZH: 海啸袭击了港口城市，造成了极大的破坏。
EN: The tsunami struck the port city, causing extensive damage.

ZH: 他们在海啸来临之前已经疏散了。
EN: They had already evacuated before the tsunami struck.

ZH: 海啸瞬间将小屋带走。
EN: The tsunami swept away the cottage in an instant.

ZH: 他们在海啸的灾难中幸存了下来。
EN: They survived the disaster of the tsunami.

ZH: 海啸袭来，带来了毁灭性的力量。
EN: The tsunami struck, bringing with it destructive force.

ZH: 他们在海啸中失去了家园。
EN: They lost their homes in the tsunami.

ZH: 海啸警报响起之后，人们开始疯狂逃散。
EN: After the tsunami warning sounded, people began to frantically flee.
